LUNCHBOX CHEESECAKE 🍰💗

This is the easiest and cheapest cheesecake recipe. All the products are easily available at home & the total cost is no more than ₹500.

Ingredients-
20 Marie Biscuits
1/2 Salted Butter Block
1kg Milk (Curdle it & save the milk solids)
1/2 Cream
4-5 drops Vanilla Essence
1-1.5 Cups Powdered Sugar
100gm Compound Chocolate

See the entire process in the video. 

DO NOT FREEZE IT. ONLY REFRIGERATE IT.
Freezing will make the biscuit layer too hard to cut. Consume within a week.

WE HAVE BEEN TOLD A LIE. 🙂
Once I went out for a lunch and made the mistake of applying sunscreen stick on my makeup. INSTANT REGRET!! IT MOVED MY MAKEUP FROM THAT SPOT!!
I was breathless and shocked!

I was told by every influencer on Instagram that a sunscreen stick doesn’t move your makeup UNTILL I TRIED IT MYSELF.

Sunscreen sticks are fine if put on a bare face but NEVER EVER EVER put it on top of your makeup! 🙏🏼😭
